# Mashup Generator â€“ Web Application

This project is a **Web-based Mashup Generator** developed as part of an academic assignment.

The application allows a user to generate an audio mashup by providing:
- Singer name
- Number of videos
- Duration of each video
- Email ID

The mashup is generated by downloading videos from YouTube, converting them into audio clips, trimming them, and merging them into a single output file.

---

##  Live Web Application Link

The project is deployed on **Render (Free Tier)** and can be accessed using the link below:

 https://mashup-project-102317022-predictive.onrender.com

> Note: Since this is a free deployment, the first load may take **30â€“50 seconds**.

---

## ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’» How to Use the Web Application

1. Open the live link provided above.
2. You will see a form titled **Mashup Generator**.
3. Fill in the following details:
   - **Singer Name**: Name of the singer (e.g., Sharry Maan)
   - **Number of Videos**: Number of YouTube videos to be used (e.g., 20)
   - **Duration of each video (seconds)**: Duration to trim from each audio (e.g., 30)
   - **Email ID**: A valid email address
4. Click on the **Submit** button.
5. The application will process the request and generate the mashup.
6. The output mashup file is prepared as per the input parameters.

